<section class="bg-white pv2 ph3 ph4-l tl min-vh-100 vh-100 w-100 dt">
  <div class="dtc v-mid">
    <h1 class="f4 f2-m f1-l fw4 lh-copy mv0 mw9 black">We’ve spent a decade knee-deep in mushrooms. This is an open invite to makers, dreamers, the ones who can see the invisible, and believe in nature’s perfect design. Join us in the space where design, biology, and the future meet.</h1>
    <p class="fw9 lh-title mt4 mb0 mw9 red" style="font-size: 8vw;">Born from Biology.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-dark-blue w-100 bg-image-gradient-1 pv5 cover">
  <p class="mv5">&nbsp;</p><!-- adds <p> tag so the <section> doesn’t collapse -->
</section>

<section class="bg-white black pv5 ph3 ph4-l tc" id="scroll-to-what-is-grow-bio">
  <h2 class="f4 f3-m f2-l lh-title fw9 mv2">What is GrowBio?</h2>
  <p class="f5 f4-l lh-copy mv2 measure center">GrowBio provides the <strong>tools</strong>, <strong>tutorials</strong>, and <strong>raw materials</strong> you need to work with biomaterials. First, we will release the mycelium kits. After that, we will be developing yeast and bacteria kits. If you work with biomaterials, this is a place to share, learn, and grow with one another!</p>
  <hr class="mv4 mw4 center">
  <p class="measure-wide center">We will be sourcing the material for our mycelium kits from <a href="https://shop.ecovativedesign.com/collections/grow-it-yourself?ref=growbio" class="code link dim red">Ecovative’s Grow-It-Yourself</a> line. Until we launch GrowBio, you can purchase legacy kits on their <a href="https://shop.ecovativedesign.com/collections/grow-it-yourself?ref=growbio" class="code link dim red">webstore</a>.</p>
</section>

